@@Rdisappearing in an endless exhibition of things that mattered once and
@@Rmatter still, which is the cruelest detail of this particular torment.
@@RLust demons haunt this shore, feeding on the lingering emotional resonance
@@Rof what the damned carry with them. They are beautiful in the way that
