The Plain of Weights~
@@RA vast grey plain extends here, extending the fourth circle's punishment into
@@Rreckless geographic scope. The stone weights the greedy push are arranged in
@@Rrows at the far end, waiting for the next rotation of sinners. Between cycles
@@Rthe plain is briefly empty, which has a quality of held breath to it that the
@@Rnext wave of screaming misers shatters thoroughly. Greed demons patrol the
@@Rperimeter with ledgers, recording the transactions of the futile -- how much
@@Rweight was pushed, how far, in what time -- compiling statistics for a report
@@Rthat will never be filed and never be read. The numbers grow very large and
@@Rthe demons take modest professional pride in keeping them accurate. The plain
@@Ris scored with the grooves of ten thousand years of stone weights dragged across it.
